  "texts": [
    "Thus, we propose future studies should use TM algorithms such as the neural topic model for image annotation, image segmentation, image classification, image detection, and event detection tasks (such as object detection, crowded scene/ video analysis, summarising video objects, tracking web video topics, extract events in videos, detecting irregular behaviours in a video scene, traffic accident detection, and activity routine discovery).",
    "• This paper recommends a continuous use of UGC to mine people's perspectives on various health cases/reactions and thus, this can be synthesized with the traditional survey findings.",
    "• The use of TM for medical records and electronic health record analysis is growing.",
    "We envisage significant growth in this area as the health domain is a high consumer of advanced technologies.",
    "However, we encourage researchers/medical practitioners should employ adequate human interpretation of TM results before deploying."
  ],
